{"type":"answer","id":15840,"parentType":"question","parentId":3462,"uid":2115,"contents":"<b>去她的微博上看了看:</b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539497636265886.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539497636265886.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539497636265886.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539497696356724.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539497696356724.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539497696356724.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539497758278014.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539497758278014.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539497758278014.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n她似乎很喜欢在微博上转发《人民日报》的文章,还经常发表一些“爱国”言论。<br>\n<br>\n也就是说——这个“莉哥OvO”,应该是一条爱党爱国的红粉蛆!<br>\n<br>\n<b>综上所述,事情的经过应该是这样的:</b><br>\n<br>\n<b>这条爱党爱国的红粉蛆,在某次直播中,情不自禁的唱起了自己深爱的“国歌”。然后,就被以莫须有的“侮辱国歌罪”拘留了5天。</b><br>\n<br>\n<b>毕竟,这首歌的作词者,都被批斗、迫害死了。</b><br>\n<br>\n<b><a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539501982698015.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539501982698015.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181014/1539501982698015.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n<br>\n<b>最后啊,奉劝那些爱党、爱国的红粉蛆们一句:</b><br>\n<br>\n<b>[b][b]实际上,那些[b]爱党、爱国的红粉蛆</b>,他们也是有一本账的,这个账是记在那儿的。一旦大清国完蛋了,这个账全给你拉出来。别看你今天爱得欢,小心啊,今后拉清单!<b>这都得应验的!头上三尺有神明,一定要有敬畏之心,[b]不要干这种事情。</b>[/b][/b][/b][/b]","date":"2018-10-14","agreeCount":19,"discussionCount":0}